Status report of Yi Tong Tse on 11/6/98

Gone through a major restructuring of the DPI code to reduce the code size
and make it more flexible.  The new code has a single decoder routine to be
shared by both the live and the ad streams.  It can also handle the general
case of splicing from one channel to another.

Improved output bit handling and added a packetizer to the DPI code to
allow transport stream output.

